<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Meemnoon Call Center - Dispatch, Transport, and Support Services">
    <title>Meemnoon Call Center</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin: 0 1rem;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .hero {
            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1200x400') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 400px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .services {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .service {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 250px;
            background: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .service h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .cta a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav ul {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Meemnoon Call Center</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Your Partner in Dispatch & Transport Services</h1>
    </section>

    <div class="container" id="services">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <div class="services">
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Dispatch Services</h3>
                <p>Efficient dispatch solutions tailored to your business needs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Transport Coordination</h3>
                <p>Seamless transport management for all types of cargo.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>24/7 Customer Support</h3>
                <p>Always available to handle your queries and issues.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Logistics Solutions</h3>
                <p>Comprehensive logistics support for smooth operations.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container cta">
        <a href="#contact">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>

    <div class="container" id="about">
        <h2>About Meemnoon</h2>
        <p>
            At Meemnoon, we specialize in providing top-notch call center services, including dispatch, transport coordination, and round-the-clock support. Our professional team ensures your operations run smoothly and efficiently. We are committed to excellence and customer satisfaction.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="container" id="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@meemnoon.com">info@meemnoon.com</a></p>
        <p>Phone: +123 456 7890</p>
        <p>Address: 123 Meemnoon Street, City, Country</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Meemnoon Call Center. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
